---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import T from '../../components/T.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="腦健康 Exposome 檢測 · Brain-Health Exposome Check-in — Matt Ye"
  description="以 2024 年 Lancet 失智症委員會 14 項可調整風險因子與空氣污染（PM2.5）累積暴露為基礎的教育性腦健康自我檢視工具。估算「腦齡加速」的教育性參考值。純前端計算，資料不上傳、不儲存。"
>
  <div class="container-wide calc-page">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="calc-hero">
      <h1><T zh="腦健康 Exposome" en="Brain-Health Exposome" /> <span class="accent-text"><T zh="檢測" en="Check-in" /></span></h1>
      <p class="calc-subtitle">
        <T
          zh="根據 2024 年《Lancet》失智症委員會的 14 項可調整風險因子，以及你一生中居住地的空氣污染（PM2.5）累積暴露，用淺白的方式看看這些「exposome（環境暴露總和）」與腦健康的關係，並給你可行動的方向。"
          en="Using the 14 modifiable risk factors from the 2024 Lancet Commission on dementia, plus the cumulative air-pollution (PM2.5) exposure across the places you've lived, see in plain terms how your lifelong 'exposome' relates to brain health — and what you can act on."
        />
      </p>
      <p class="calc-privacy">🔒 <T zh="所有計算都在你的瀏覽器內完成，資料不會上傳或儲存到任何伺服器。" en="All calculations run entirely in your browser — nothing is uploaded or stored on any server." /></p>
    </section>

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <section class="calc-disclaimer">
      <p><strong><T zh="⚠️ 重要提醒：" en="⚠️ Important: " /></strong><T zh="本工具僅供一般健康教育與自我覺察之用，並非醫療器材、不是診斷或篩檢工具，無法預測任何人是否會罹患失智症。" en="This tool is for general health education and self-awareness only. It is not a medical device, not a diagnostic or screening test, and cannot predict whether anyone will develop dementia." /></p>
      <ul>
        <li><T zh="結果描述的是「族群層級」的關聯（來自已發表研究），而不是對「你個人」的預測；同樣的因子，每個人的結果差異其實很大。" en="Results describe population-level associations (from published research), not a prediction about you personally — individual outcomes vary a great deal." /></li>
        <li><T zh="這裡的「腦齡加速」是一個教育性的比喻數字，不是用腦部影像（MRI／EEG）量出來的真實腦齡。" en="The 'brain-age acceleration' here is an educational illustration, not a real brain age measured from imaging (MRI/EEG)." /></li>
        <li><T zh="本工具不能取代醫療專業判斷。如有任何健康疑慮，請諮詢合格的醫療人員。" en="This does not replace professional medical advice. Consult a qualified healthcare provider for any health concern." /></li>
        <li><T zh="PM2.5 採用 ACAG 衛星推估的逐年（1998–2024）縣市資料（1998 年以前的居住年份沿用 1998 值）。地圖上的失智盛行率為縣市層級的模型估計值，非實測。" en="PM2.5 uses ACAG satellite-derived annual (1998–2024) county data (residence years before 1998 reuse the 1998 value). The dementia prevalence on the map is a county-level modelled estimate, not measured." /></li>
        <li><T zh="為了少填一步，第一段居住地的「國家」會依你目前的網路所在地或瀏覽器語系自動預設（不經第三方、不會索取定位權限），你可以隨時自行更改。所有計算都在你的瀏覽器完成，不會上傳。" en="To save a step, the first residence's country is pre-filled from your current network location or browser locale (no third party, no location-permission prompt); you can change it anytime. All calculations run in your browser and nothing is uploaded." /></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Wizard -->
    <div class="wizard">
      <ol class="wizard-steps" id="wizard-steps">
        <li data-step="1" class="is-active"><span class="wz-dot">1</span><span class="wz-lbl"><T zh="基本資料" en="About you" /></span></li>
        <li data-step="2"><span class="wz-dot">2</span><span class="wz-lbl"><T zh="居住史" en="Places" /></span></li>
        <li data-step="3"><span class="wz-dot">3</span><span class="wz-lbl"><T zh="健康與生活" en="Health" /></span></li>
        <li data-step="4"><span class="wz-dot">4</span><span class="wz-lbl"><T zh="結果" en="Results" /></span></li>
      </ol>

      <!-- Step 1 — About you -->
      <section class="wizard-step is-active" data-step="1">
        <p class="section-heading">1. <T zh="關於你" en="About you" /></p>
        <div class="calc-form-card">
          <div class="form-grid">
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="年齡" en="Age (years)" /></span>
              <input type="number" id="in-age" value="50" min="18" max="100" step="1" />
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="生理性別" en="Sex" /></span>
              <select id="in-sex">
                <option value="female" data-zh="女性" data-en="Female">女性</option>
                <option value="male" data-zh="男性" data-en="Male">男性</option>
              </select>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="教育程度" en="Education" /> <em><T zh="（認知存量）" en="(cognitive reserve)" /></em></span>
              <select id="in-education">
                <option value="tertiary" data-zh="大專以上" data-en="Tertiary or above">大專以上</option>
                <option value="secondary" data-zh="高中職" data-en="Secondary (high school)">高中職</option>
                <option value="primary" data-zh="國中以下" data-en="Primary or less">國中以下</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="指早年正規教育年數；只有「國中以下」才計為風險。終身學習也能累積認知存量" en="Early-life schooling; only 'primary or less' counts as a risk. Lifelong learning also builds reserve" /></small>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="wizard-nav">
          <span></span>
          <button type="button" class="wz-btn wz-next" data-goto="2"><T zh="下一步 →" en="Next →" /></button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 2 — Places -->
      <section class="wizard-step" data-step="2">
        <p class="section-heading">2. <T zh="你住過的地方" en="Places you've lived" /></p>
        <p class="calc-section-desc">
          <T zh="加入你人生各階段主要居住的縣市與大約年份。系統會用該地區的年均 PM2.5 估算你「時間加權」的長期空氣污染暴露。年份可粗估即可。" en="Add the main counties you've lived in across life, with rough years. We estimate your time-weighted long-term PM2.5 exposure from each area's annual mean. Approximate years are fine." />
        </p>
        <div class="supp-table-wrap">
          <table class="supp-table res-table">
            <colgroup>
              <col class="col-country" />
              <col class="col-region" />
              <col class="col-year" />
              <col class="col-year" />
              <col class="col-pm" />
              <col class="col-del" />
            </colgroup>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th><T zh="國家" en="Country" /></th>
                <th><T zh="地區" en="Region" /></th>
                <th><T zh="從" en="From" /></th>
                <th><T zh="到" en="To" /></th>
                <th>PM2.5</th>
                <th></th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="res-grid"></tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="res-controls">
          <button type="button" class="wz-btn wz-ghost" id="res-add">+ <T zh="新增一段居住" en="Add a place" /></button>
          <p class="res-summary" id="res-summary"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="wizard-nav">
          <button type="button" class="wz-btn wz-back" data-goto="1">← <T zh="上一步" en="Back" /></button>
          <button type="button" class="wz-btn wz-next" data-goto="3"><T zh="下一步 →" en="Next →" /></button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 3 — Health & lifestyle -->
      <section class="wizard-step" data-step="3">
        <p class="section-heading">3. <T zh="健康與生活型態" en="Health & lifestyle" /></p>
        <p class="calc-section-desc"><T zh="不確定就選「不確定」，不會被算成風險。這些對應到 Lancet 委員會可調整的失智風險因子。" en="Pick 'Not sure' if you don't know — it won't be counted as a risk. These map to the Lancet Commission's modifiable dementia risk factors." /></p>

        <div class="calc-form-card">
          <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="👂 感官" en="👂 Sensory" /></p>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="聽力損失" en="Hearing loss" /></span>
              <select id="in-hearing">
                <option value="none" data-zh="沒有" data-en="No">沒有</option>
                <option value="untreated" data-zh="有，未使用助聽器" data-en="Yes, untreated">有，未使用助聽器</option>
                <option value="treated" data-zh="有，已矯治／戴助聽器" data-en="Yes, treated / aids">有，已矯治／戴助聽器</option>
                <option value="unknown" data-zh="不確定" data-en="Not sure">不確定</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="「未矯治」= 聽得吃力／需調大音量但沒戴助聽器。矯治後風險大幅下降" en="'Untreated' = struggle to hear but no hearing aid. Treating it lowers the risk a lot" /></small>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="視力損失" en="Vision loss" /></span>
              <select id="in-vision">
                <option value="none" data-zh="沒有" data-en="No">沒有</option>
                <option value="untreated" data-zh="有，未矯治" data-en="Yes, untreated">有，未矯治</option>
                <option value="treated" data-zh="有，已矯治（眼鏡／手術）" data-en="Yes, corrected">有，已矯治（眼鏡／手術）</option>
                <option value="unknown" data-zh="不確定" data-en="Not sure">不確定</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="「未矯治」= 可治療的視力問題（如白內障）未處理。戴眼鏡／手術矯正即算已矯治" en="'Untreated' = treatable vision loss (e.g. cataract) left uncorrected. Glasses/surgery count as corrected" /></small>
            </label>
          </div>

          <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="❤️ 心血管代謝" en="❤️ Cardiometabolic" /></p>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="高血壓" en="Hypertension" /></span>
              <select id="in-htn">
                <option value="no" data-zh="沒有" data-en="No">沒有</option>
                <option value="yes" data-zh="有" data-en="Yes">有</option>
                <option value="unknown" data-zh="不確定" data-en="Not sure">不確定</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="經診斷高血壓，或血壓 ≥ 140/90 mmHg（中年高血壓與失智關聯最強）" en="Diagnosed, or BP ≥ 140/90 mmHg (midlife hypertension matters most)" /></small>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="糖尿病" en="Diabetes" /></span>
              <select id="in-diabetes">
                <option value="no" data-zh="沒有" data-en="No">沒有</option>
                <option value="yes" data-zh="有" data-en="Yes">有</option>
                <option value="unknown" data-zh="不確定" data-en="Not sure">不確定</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="經診斷，或 HbA1c ≥ 6.5% / 空腹血糖 ≥ 126 mg/dL" en="Diagnosed, or HbA1c ≥ 6.5% / fasting glucose ≥ 126 mg/dL" /></small>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="體位（BMI）" en="Body weight (BMI)" /></span>
              <select id="in-bmi">
                <option value="normal" data-zh="正常或過輕" data-en="Normal or under">正常或過輕</option>
                <option value="overweight" data-zh="過重" data-en="Overweight">過重</option>
                <option value="obese" data-zh="肥胖（BMI ≥ 30）" data-en="Obese (BMI ≥ 30)">肥胖（BMI ≥ 30）</option>
                <option value="unknown" data-zh="不確定" data-en="Not sure">不確定</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="台灣：過重 BMI 24–27、肥胖 ≥ 27（國際肥胖為 ≥ 30）。中年肥胖較相關" en="Overweight BMI 24–27, obese ≥ 27 (Taiwan); ≥ 30 is the international obesity cutoff" /></small>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="膽固醇（LDL 高不高）" en="Cholesterol (is LDL high)" /></span>
              <select id="in-cholesterol">
                <option value="normal" data-zh="正常或不確定" data-en="Normal or unsure">正常或不確定</option>
                <option value="high" data-zh="LDL 偏高" data-en="High LDL">LDL 偏高</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="不知道數值就用這裡；建議 LDL < 130 mg/dL" en="Use this if you don't know your number; aim for LDL < 130 mg/dL" /></small>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="LDL 數值（選填，更精準）" en="LDL value (optional, more precise)" /></span>
              <div class="ldl-row">
                <input type="number" id="in-ldl" placeholder="130" min="40" max="300" step="1" />
                <select id="in-ldl-unit" class="ldl-unit">
                  <option value="mgdl" data-zh="mg/dL" data-en="mg/dL">mg/dL</option>
                  <option value="mmol" data-zh="mmol/L" data-en="mmol/L">mmol/L</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="建議 < 130 mg/dL（≈ 3.36 mmol/L）；心血管高風險者目標更低。台灣／美國檢驗單多為 mg/dL" en="Aim for < 130 mg/dL (≈ 3.36 mmol/L); lower if high cardiovascular risk. TW/US labs report mg/dL" /></small>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="身體活動" en="Physical activity" /></span>
              <select id="in-inactive">
                <option value="active" data-zh="每週規律運動" data-en="Regularly active">每週規律運動</option>
                <option value="inactive" data-zh="很少運動" data-en="Rarely active">很少運動</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="「規律」≈ 每週 ≥ 150 分鐘中等強度（如快走）。低於此算很少運動" en="'Regular' ≈ ≥ 150 min/week moderate (e.g. brisk walking); below that counts as rarely active" /></small>
            </label>
          </div>

          <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="🧠 心理健康" en="🧠 Mental health" /></p>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="憂鬱症" en="Depression" /></span>
              <select id="in-depression">
                <option value="no" data-zh="沒有" data-en="No">沒有</option>
                <option value="yes" data-zh="有（曾被診斷）" data-en="Yes (diagnosed)">有（曾被診斷）</option>
                <option value="unknown" data-zh="不確定" data-en="Not sure">不確定</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="曾被醫療診斷憂鬱症，或長期情緒低落／就醫用藥。偶爾心情不好不算" en="Diagnosed depression, or persistent low mood / treatment. Occasional low mood doesn't count" /></small>
            </label>
          </div>

          <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="🤝 社會與認知" en="🤝 Social & cognitive" /></p>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="社交孤立" en="Social isolation" /></span>
              <select id="in-isolation">
                <option value="connected" data-zh="常有社交往來" data-en="Socially connected">常有社交往來</option>
                <option value="isolated" data-zh="較少與人往來" data-en="Socially isolated">較少與人往來</option>
                <option value="unknown" data-zh="不確定" data-en="Not sure">不確定</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="獨居、很少與家人朋友往來、缺乏規律社交活動 → 較孤立" en="Living alone, little contact with family/friends, few regular social activities → isolated" /></small>
            </label>
          </div>

          <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="🚬 生活型態與外傷" en="🚬 Lifestyle & injury" /></p>
          <div class="form-grid">
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="吸菸" en="Smoking" /></span>
              <select id="in-smoking">
                <option value="never" data-zh="從不吸菸" data-en="Never">從不吸菸</option>
                <option value="former" data-zh="已戒菸" data-en="Former smoker">已戒菸</option>
                <option value="current" data-zh="目前吸菸" data-en="Current smoker">目前吸菸</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="任何時候戒菸都有幫助；戒菸後風險會隨時間下降" en="Quitting helps at any age; risk keeps falling after you stop" /></small>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="飲酒" en="Alcohol" /></span>
              <select id="in-alcohol">
                <option value="moderate" data-zh="不喝或適量" data-en="None or moderate">不喝或適量</option>
                <option value="heavy" data-zh="過量（每週 &gt; 21 份）" data-en="Heavy (&gt; 21 units/wk)">過量（每週 &gt; 21 份）</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="過量 ≈ 每週 > 21 英制單位（≈ 每週 > 10 杯酒／2 瓶紅酒）" en="Heavy ≈ > 21 UK units/week (≈ > 10 drinks / 2 bottles of wine a week)" /></small>
            </label>
            <label class="form-field">
              <span><T zh="頭部外傷" en="Head injury (TBI)" /></span>
              <select id="in-tbi">
                <option value="no" data-zh="沒有" data-en="No">沒有</option>
                <option value="yes" data-zh="曾有明顯頭部外傷" data-en="Yes, significant TBI">曾有明顯頭部外傷</option>
              </select>
              <small class="field-hint"><T zh="曾因撞擊昏迷／就醫的明顯腦部外傷（如車禍、跌倒、運動撞擊）" en="A significant TBI with loss of consciousness / medical care (crash, fall, sports impact)" /></small>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="wizard-nav">
          <button type="button" class="wz-btn wz-back" data-goto="2">← <T zh="上一步" en="Back" /></button>
          <button type="button" class="wz-btn wz-next" data-goto="4"><T zh="看結果 →" en="See results →" /></button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Step 4 — Results -->
      <section class="wizard-step" data-step="4">
        <p class="section-heading">4. <T zh="你的結果" en="Your results" /></p>

        <div class="result-profile" id="out-profile"></div>

        <div class="result-brainage">
          <div class="ba-label"><T zh="教育性「腦齡加速」估計" en="Educational 'brain-age acceleration' estimate" /></div>
          <div class="ba-gauge" id="out-gauge"></div>
          <div class="ba-num" id="out-brainage">—</div>
          <div class="ba-caption" id="out-brainage-caption"></div>
          <div id="out-brainage-detail"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="cat-head">
          <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="各面向風險換算腦齡老化概況" en="Brain-aging by domain (risk-converted)" /></p>
          <div class="cat-toggle" role="group" aria-label="display style">
            <button type="button" class="cat-view-btn is-active" data-view="radar"><T zh="雷達圖" en="Radar" /></button>
            <button type="button" class="cat-view-btn" data-view="list"><T zh="清單" en="List" /></button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <figure class="cat-radar" id="out-radar"></figure>
        <div class="stat-list" id="out-categories"></div>

        <div class="result-exposome" id="out-exposome"></div>

        <p class="calc-subheading"><T zh="你的風險因子：說明與建議" en="Your flagged factors: what they mean & what to do" /></p>
        <ul class="action-list" id="out-actions"></ul>

        <div class="wizard-nav">
          <button type="button" class="wz-btn wz-back" data-goto="3">← <T zh="修改答案" en="Edit answers" /></button>
          <span></span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Regional map (Taiwan / Japan / Korea / China / USA / India) -->
    <section class="calc-section map-section">
      <p class="section-heading"><T zh="地圖：空污與失智概況" en="Map: air pollution & dementia" /></p>
      <p class="calc-section-desc"><T zh="切換國家（涵蓋亞洲、歐洲、美洲、大洋洲等 20 多國）與圖層，看各行政區近年的 PM2.5；色階以 WHO 標準（≤5 µg/m³）為基準，可跨國比較。台灣另有縣市層級的失智盛行「模型估計值」。把游標移到區域上看數值。" en="Switch country (20+ across Asia, Europe, the Americas and Oceania) and layer to see recent PM2.5 by district, on a WHO-anchored scale (≤5 µg/m³) that's comparable across countries. Taiwan also has a county-level MODELLED dementia-prevalence estimate. Hover a district for values." /></p>
      <div class="map-controls">
        <label class="map-country-wrap">
          <span class="map-country-label"><T zh="國家／地區" en="Country / region" /></span>
          <select id="map-country" class="map-country">
            <optgroup data-zh="東亞" data-en="East Asia" label="東亞">
